<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <% include partials/header %>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@300;400;600&family=Karla:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --gold: #c9963a;
      --gold-light: #e8bc68;
      --deep: #1a0f00;
      --cream: #fdf6ec;
      --muted: #8a7560;
      --text: #3a2810;
    }
 
    .timeline-page {
      background: var(--cream);
      color: var(--text);
      font-family: 'Karla', sans-serif;
      padding-bottom: 40px;
    }
 
    /* Header */
    .timeline-header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 40px 24px 36px;
      position: relative;
    }
 
    .timeline-header::after {
      content: '';
      display: block;
      width: 60px;
      height: 2px;
      background: var(--gold);
      margin: 24px auto 0;
    }
 
    .temple-name {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 4vw, 2.2rem);
      font-weight: 300;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      color: var(--deep);
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
 
    .subtitle {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.25em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--gold);
      margin-top: 8px;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
 
    /* Timeline wrapper */
    .timeline {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 24px 40px;
      position: relative;
    }
 
    .timeline::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      left: 50%;
      top: 0;
      bottom: 0;
      width: 2px;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, var(--gold) 5%, var(--gold) 95%, transparent);
      transform: translateX(-50%);
    }
 
    /* Each entry */
    .entry {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 48px 1fr;
      align-items: start;
      gap: 0;
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }
 
    .entry:nth-child(odd) .content {
      grid-column: 1;
      text-align: right;
      padding-right: 32px;
    }
 
    .entry:nth-child(odd) .spacer { grid-column: 3; }
 
    .entry:nth-child(even) .content {
      grid-column: 3;
      text-align: left;
      padding-left: 32px;
      order: 3;
    }
 
    .entry:nth-child(even) .spacer { grid-column: 1; order: 1; }
 
    .node-col {
      grid-column: 2;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      padding-top: 20px;
      order: 2;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
    }
 
    .node {
      width: 16px;
      height: 16px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--cream);
      border: 2px solid var(--gold);
      position: relative;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
 
    .node::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: -5px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
      transition: border-color 0.3s;
    }
 
    .spacer { min-height: 80px; }
 
    /* Content — using <details>/<summary> for expand/collapse */
    .content {
      padding-top: 8px;
      padding-bottom: 32px;
    }
 
    .content details {
      list-style: none;
    }
 
    .content summary {
      list-style: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      outline: none;
    }
 
    .content summary::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }
 
    .content details[open] .node-hint { display: none; }
 
    .year-tag {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 2.4rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--gold);
      line-height: 1;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      transition: color 0.3s;
    }
 
    .content details[open] .year-tag,
    .content summary:hover .year-tag {
      color: var(--deep);
    }
 
    .title {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--deep);
      margin-top: 6px;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }
 
    .detail {
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }
 
    .significance {
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      color: var(--gold);
      font-style: italic;
      margin-top: 6px;
    }
 
    /* Subtle indicator that entry is expandable */
    .node-hint {
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--gold-light);
      margin-top: 4px;
      opacity: 0.8;
    }
 
    /* Hover — highlight the node when hovering content */
    .content:hover ~ .node-col .node,
    .content summary:hover ~ * .node {
      background: var(--gold);
      transform: scale(1.3);
    }
 
    /* Mobile */
    @media (max-width: 560px) {
      .timeline::before { left: 20px; }
      .entry { grid-template-columns: 40px 1fr; }
      .entry:nth-child(odd) .content,
      .entry:nth-child(even) .content {
        grid-column: 2;
        text-align: left;
        padding-left: 24px;
        padding-right: 0;
        order: 2;
      }
      .node-col { grid-column: 1; order: 1; padding-top: 14px; justify-content: flex-start; padding-left: 13px; }
      .entry:nth-child(odd) .spacer,
      .entry:nth-child(even) .spacer { display: none; }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <% include partials/menu %>
  <div class="container bg-light">
    <div class="timeline-page">
      <div class="timeline-header">
        <p class="subtitle">A Journey of Faith</p>
        <h1 class="temple-name">Shree Swaminarayan Mandir Bhuj &mdash; Sydney</h1>
      </div>
 
      <div class="timeline">
 
        <!-- Entry 1 -->
        <div class="entry">
          <div class="content">
            <details>
              <summary>
                <div class="year-tag">Early 2000s</div>
                <div class="title">Seeds of Satsang</div>
                <div class="node-hint">Tap to expand</div>
              </summary>
              <div class="detail">Devotees began performing daily rituals and sabhas in homes, building the foundation of a community before a dedicated space existed.</div>
              <div class="significance">The beginning of a spiritual home in Sydney.</div>
            </details>
          </div>
          <div class="node-col"><div class="node"></div></div>
          <div class="spacer"></div>
        </div>
 
        <!-- Entry 2 -->
        <div class="entry">
          <div class="spacer"></div>
          <div class="node-col"><div class="node"></div></div>
          <div class="content">
            <details>
              <summary>
                <div class="year-tag">2001</div>
                <div class="title">Formal Registration</div>
                <div class="node-hint">Tap to expand</div>
              </summary>
              <div class="detail">Under guidance of Late Pujya Mahant Sadguru Purani Swami Hariswarupdasji, Shree Swaminarayan Temple Sydney Inc. was registered as a non-profit organisation.</div>
              <div class="significance">A formal structure to support growing activities and festivals.</div>
            </details>
          </div>
        </div>
 
        <!-- Entry 3 -->
        <div class="entry">
          <div class="content">
            <details>
              <summary>
                <div class="year-tag">2003</div>
                <div class="title">Youth &amp; Language</div>
                <div class="node-hint">Tap to expand</div>
              </summary>
              <div class="detail">SSYM Sydney was established in the presence of esteemed Swamis from Bhuj &mdash; the first international branch of the Yuvak Mandal. Ghanshyam Gujarati classes also began.</div>
              <div class="significance">Youth engagement and cultural education took root.</div>
            </details>
          </div>
          <div class="node-col"><div class="node"></div></div>
          <div class="spacer"></div>
        </div>
 
        <!-- Entry 4 -->
        <div class="entry">
          <div class="spacer"></div>
          <div class="node-col"><div class="node"></div></div>
          <div class="content">
            <details>
              <summary>
                <div class="year-tag">2012</div>
                <div class="title">A Permanent Home</div>
                <div class="node-hint">Tap to expand</div>
              </summary>
              <div class="detail">A new site was secured after earlier setbacks. Bhoomi Poojan and Khat Muhurat were conducted in April in the presence of His Holiness Mota Maharajshree Tejendraprasadji Maharaj.</div>
              <div class="significance">A landmark step toward a permanent spiritual home.</div>
            </details>
          </div>
        </div>
 
        <!-- Entry 5 -->
        <div class="entry">
          <div class="content">
            <details>
              <summary>
                <div class="year-tag">2013</div>
                <div class="title">Grand Opening</div>
                <div class="node-hint">Tap to expand</div>
              </summary>
              <div class="detail">Construction completed in nine months. On January 18, His Holiness Acharya Maharajshree Koshalendraprasadji presided over the Murti Pran Pratishtha. GBM, Gujarati classes, and the Nilkanth Pipe Band &amp; Lazium were all established.</div>
              <div class="significance">A landmark year of inauguration and new beginnings.</div>
            </details>
          </div>
          <div class="node-col"><div class="node"></div></div>
          <div class="spacer"></div>
        </div>
 
        <!-- Entry 6 -->
        <div class="entry">
          <div class="spacer"></div>
          <div class="node-col"><div class="node"></div></div>
          <div class="content">
            <details>
              <summary>
                <div class="year-tag">2014</div>
                <div class="title">Dharmik Education</div>
                <div class="node-hint">Tap to expand</div>
              </summary>
              <div class="detail">Ghanshyam Dharmik classes launched using Bhuj Mandir materials, providing structured values-based education for children.</div>
              <div class="significance">Spiritual education for the next generation commenced.</div>
            </details>
          </div>
        </div>
 
        <!-- Entry 7 -->
        <div class="entry">
          <div class="content">
            <details>
              <summary>
                <div class="year-tag">2018</div>
                <div class="title">Shikhar Bandh Renovation</div>
                <div class="node-hint">Tap to expand</div>
              </summary>
              <div class="detail">Significant renovations transformed the temple into a shikhar bandh structure adorned with a beautiful pink stone facade. GBM refreshed with a new logo and updated materials.</div>
              <div class="significance">Facilities and branding updated to support future growth.</div>
            </details>
          </div>
          <div class="node-col"><div class="node"></div></div>
          <div class="spacer"></div>
        </div>
 
        <!-- Entry 8 -->
        <div class="entry">
          <div class="spacer"></div>
          <div class="node-col"><div class="node"></div></div>
          <div class="content">
            <details>
              <summary>
                <div class="year-tag">2019</div>
                <div class="title">Music Blossoms</div>
                <div class="node-hint">Tap to expand</div>
              </summary>
              <div class="detail">Ghanshyam Music classes expanded to include tabla, keyboard, and singing, deepening connection to the Sampraday&rsquo;s heritage.</div>
              <div class="significance">Broader musical engagement for youth and community.</div>
            </details>
          </div>
        </div>
 
        <!-- Entry 9 -->
        <div class="entry">
          <div class="content">
            <details>
              <summary>
                <div class="year-tag">2022</div>
                <div class="title">Unity &amp; Alignment</div>
                <div class="node-hint">Tap to expand</div>
              </summary>
              <div class="detail">The Svadhyay international syllabus was introduced. The temple officially aligned under Bhuj Mandir &mdash; Sydney was the first temple worldwide to adopt the SSMB name.</div>
              <div class="significance">Deepening of study and formal global affiliation.</div>
            </details>
          </div>
          <div class="node-col"><div class="node"></div></div>
          <div class="spacer"></div>
        </div>
 
        <!-- Entry 10 -->
        <div class="entry">
          <div class="spacer"></div>
          <div class="node-col"><div class="node"></div></div>
          <div class="content">
            <details>
              <summary>
                <div class="year-tag">2023</div>
                <div class="title">International Stage</div>
                <div class="node-hint">Tap to expand</div>
              </summary>
              <div class="detail">The Nilkanth Pipe Band performed at the 200-year anniversary of Bhuj Mandir in India. The Svadhyay syllabus continued to shape youth education.</div>
              <div class="significance">International recognition and sustained educational focus.</div>
            </details>
          </div>
        </div>
 
        <!-- Entry 11 -->
        <div class="entry">
          <div class="content">
            <details>
              <summary>
                <div class="year-tag">2024</div>
                <div class="title">Record Enrolment</div>
                <div class="node-hint">Tap to expand</div>
              </summary>
              <div class="detail">210 students enrolled across GBM programmes &mdash; the highest participation ever across Dharmik, Gujarati, and Music streams.</div>
              <div class="significance">A thriving community of learners and spiritual seekers.</div>
            </details>
          </div>
          <div class="node-col"><div class="node"></div></div>
          <div class="spacer"></div>
        </div>
 
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
   <% include partials/footer %>
</body>
</html>
